---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import SectionDivider from "../components/SectionDivider.astro";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";

const scheduleUrl = "https://homeopathyhelpnow.com/services/";

const contactEmail =
  "mailto:Mindy@DivineHealthHomeopathy.com?subject=Consultation%20Inquiry&body=Hello%20Mindy%2C%0A%0AI%20would%20like%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20classical%20homeopathy%20and%20working%20with%20you.%0A%0AThe%20health%20concerns%20I%20am%20seeking%20support%20with%20are%3A%0A%0A";
---

<Layout
  title="Homeopathic Consultations | Divine Health Homeopathy"
  description="Learn what to expect from an individualized classical homeopathy consultation with Mindy Wallent, including the discovery call, telehealth intake, case analysis, remedy recommendation, and follow-up care."
>
  <main>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="consultation-hero">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <p class="eyebrow">Your Healing Journey</p>

        <h1>Every healing journey begins with listening.</h1>

        <div class="divider-wrap">
          <SectionDivider />
        </div>

        <p class="hero-copy">
          Healing begins long before a remedy is chosen. Every consultation is
          a thoughtful conversation designed to understand you as a whole
          person&mdash;your health, your experiences, your story, and the
          symptoms that make your case unlike anyone else&rsquo;s.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-actions">
          <Button
            href={scheduleUrl}
            target="_blank"
            variant="primary"
          >
            Schedule a Consultation
          </Button>

          <Button href={contactEmail} variant="gold">
            Contact Mindy
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Hahnemann quote -->
    <section class="quote-section">
  <div class="quote-inner">
    <span
      class="quote-mark quote-mark-open"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
      &ldquo;
    </span>

    <blockquote>
      <p>
        The highest ideal of cure is the rapid, gentle, and permanent
        restoration of health.<span
          class="quote-mark-close-inline"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >&rdquo;</span>
      </p>

      <cite>
        Samuel Hahnemann,
        <em>Organon of Medicine</em>,
        Aphorism 2
      </cite>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>


    <!-- What makes a consultation different -->
    <section class="difference-section">
      <div class="difference-inner">
        <div class="difference-heading">
          <p class="eyebrow">Individualized Care</p>

          <h2>What makes a homeopathic consultation different?</h2>

          <div class="divider-left">
            <SectionDivider />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="difference-copy">
          <p>
            Many healthcare appointments focus primarily on identifying and
            managing a particular diagnosis. Classical homeopathy also seeks to
            understand the person who is experiencing the symptoms.
          </p>

          <p>
            Your physical concerns, health history, emotional responses,
            personal tendencies, and individual experiences all contribute to
            the complete picture of your case.
          </p>

          <p class="emphasis">
            The goal is not simply to find a remedy associated with a
            diagnosis. The goal is to identify the remedy that most closely
            matches the unintegrated energy at the forefront of your case.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Process introduction -->
    <section class="process-intro">
      <div class="process-intro-inner">
        <p class="eyebrow">What to Expect</p>

        <h2>A thoughtful process centered on your unique story.</h2>

        <SectionDivider />

        <p>
          Every consultation follows the same general path, but no two cases
          are approached in exactly the same way. Your first appointment
          provides the time needed to understand your health history before an
          individualized recommendation is carefully considered.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Consultation timeline -->
    <section class="timeline-section">
      <div class="timeline">

        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <article class="timeline-step step-left">
          <div class="timeline-marker" aria-hidden="true">
            <span>1</span>
          </div>

          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-heading">
              <p class="step-label">The First Conversation</p>

              <p class="step-duration">
                Approximately 15 minutes
              </p>
            </div>

            <h3>Discovery Call</h3>

            <p>
              If you are new to homeopathy or wondering whether it may be a
              good fit, a complimentary discovery call is a comfortable place
              to begin.
            </p>

            <p>During this conversation, you can:</p>

            <ul>
              <li>Meet Mindy and ask questions.</li>
              <li>Learn more about individualized classical homeopathy.</li>
              <li>Briefly discuss what you are seeking support with.</li>
              <li>Decide whether moving forward feels right for you.</li>
            </ul>

            <p class="step-note">
              There is no obligation. Sometimes the most important first step
              is simply having a conversation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>


        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <article class="timeline-step step-right">
          <div class="timeline-marker" aria-hidden="true">
            <span>2</span>
          </div>

          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-heading">
              <p class="step-label">Your Complete Health Story</p>

              <p class="step-duration">
                Approximately 1&ndash;2 hours
              </p>
            </div>

            <h3>Initial Telehealth Consultation</h3>

            <p>
              Your journey begins with a relaxed consultation from the comfort
              of your own home. Through a telehealth video appointment,
              we&rsquo;ll explore your health history, current concerns,
              lifestyle, and the experiences that make your case unique.
            </p>

            <p>Topics include:</p>

            <ul class="two-column-list">
              <li>Current health concerns</li>
              <li>Past illnesses and treatments</li>
              <li>Childhood health</li>
              <li>Sleep and energy</li>
              <li>Food preferences and sensitivities</li>
              <li>Stress responses</li>
              <li>Emotional patterns</li>
              <li>Family health history</li>
              <li>What improves or aggravates symptoms</li>
              <li>And anything else you feel is relevant</li>
            </ul>

            <p class="step-note">
              Some questions may seem unusual at first, but each detail helps
              build a more complete understanding of your individual symptom
              picture.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>


        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <article class="timeline-step step-left">
          <div class="timeline-marker" aria-hidden="true">
            <span>3</span>
          </div>

          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-heading">
              <p class="step-label">Work Behind the Scenes</p>
            </div>

            <h3>Careful Case Analysis</h3>

            <p>
              After the consultation ends, the work continues. Your case is
              reviewed and studied using the principles of classical
              homeopathy.
            </p>

            <p>
              This includes repertory analysis, study of the
              homeopathic materia medica, comparison of possible remedies, and so much more that contribute to the
              careful consideration of the details that distinguish your case.
            </p>

            <div class="principles">
              <span>No protocols</span>
              <span>No one-size-fits-all plans</span>
              <span>Every case analyzed throughly</span>
            </div>

            <p class="step-note">
              As a supervised student practitioner, Mindy&rsquo;s case analysis
              and recommendations are reviewed with experienced professional
              classical homeopaths through Homeopathy Help Network.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>


        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <article class="timeline-step step-right">
          <div class="timeline-marker" aria-hidden="true">
            <span>4</span>
          </div>

          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-heading">
              <p class="step-label">Your Individualized Plan</p>
            </div>

            <h3>Remedy Recommendation</h3>

            <p>
              Once the analysis is complete, you will receive a remedy recommendation
            along with clear instructions.
            </p>

            <p>Your recommendation includes:</p>

            <ul>
              <li>The selected homeopathic remedy and potency.</li>
              <li>Where to purchase the remedy.</li>
              <li>Instructions for taking the remedy.</li>
              <li>Guidance about what to observe afterward.</li>
              <li>Information about when to follow up.</li>
            </ul>

            <p class="step-note">
              Homeopathic remedies are not selected solely by diagnosis.
              Recommendations are based on the complete and individualized
              picture developed during your consultation and case analysis.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>


        <!-- Step 5 -->
        <article class="timeline-step step-left">
          <div class="timeline-marker" aria-hidden="true">
            <span>5</span>
          </div>

          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-heading">
              <p class="step-label">Continued Partnership</p>
            </div>

            <h3>Follow-Up Care</h3>

            <p>
              Healing is a process rather than a single appointment. Follow-up
              consultations provide an opportunity to evaluate how your health
              and symptoms are changing over time.
            </p>

            <p>
              During follow-up care, Mindy will listen for meaningful changes,
              review your response, and determine whether the current remedy
              should be continued, repeated, adjusted, or simply allowed more
              time.
            </p>

            <p class="step-note">
              The focus remains on thoughtful observation and respecting the pace of your healing process.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Is homeopathy right for me -->
    <section class="right-for-me">

      <div class="right-for-me-inner">
        <div class="right-for-me-copy">
          <p class="eyebrow">An Individualized Approach</p>

          <h2>Is classical homeopathy right for me?</h2>

          <div class="gold-divider" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="gold-line gold-line-left"></span>

            <span class="gold-fleur">
              &#9884;
            </span>

            <span class="gold-line gold-line-right"></span>
          </div>

          <p>
            Classical homeopathy appeals to individuals and families seeking
            care that considers their complete health story rather than
            focusing only on isolated symptoms.
          </p>

          <p>
            People explore homeopathy for acute or short illnesses like colds, or sprains, long-standing concerns, recurring
            patterns of feeling unwell, periods of change such as hormonal processes of life, and/or a desire to support their overall
            well-being through a more individualized approach.
          </p>

          <p>
            Every case is different. A discovery call can help you ask
            questions and decide whether this approach feels appropriate for
            your goals.
          </p>
        </div>

        <aside class="reassurance-card">
          <p class="card-eyebrow">Important to Know</p>

          <h3>
            Homeopathy works alongside appropriate medical care.
          </h3>

          <p>
            Mindy does not diagnose medical conditions or advise clients to
            discontinue prescribed medications. Medication changes and medical
            decisions should always be discussed with the prescribing
            healthcare professional.
          </p>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Consultation FAQ -->
    <section class="consultation-faq">
      <div class="faq-inner">
        <header class="faq-heading">
          <p class="eyebrow">Common Questions</p>

          <h2>Questions about consultations</h2>

          <SectionDivider />

          <p>
            These answers cover a few of the questions clients commonly have
            before care begins.
          </p>
        </header>

        <div class="faq-list">

          <details>
            <summary>
              <span>How long is the first consultation?</span>
              <span class="faq-symbol" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
            </summary>

            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>
                Initial consultations generally last between one and two hours.
                This provides enough time to explore your current concerns,
                health history, patterns, and individual experiences without
                feeling rushed.
              </p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details>
            <summary>
              <span>Are consultations conducted virtually?</span>
              <span class="faq-symbol" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
            </summary>

            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>
                Yes. Consultations are conducted through telehealth video
                appointments, allowing you to participate from the comfort and
                privacy of your own home.
              </p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details>
            <summary>
              <span>Will I receive a remedy during my appointment?</span>
              <span class="faq-symbol" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
            </summary>

            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>
                Usually not during the appointment itself. Your complete case
                is reviewed afterward so the recommendation can be made
                thoughtfully and discussed through the supervision process.
              </p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details>
            <summary>
              <span>Do I need to stop taking my medications?</span>
              <span class="faq-symbol" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
            </summary>

            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>
                No. Do not discontinue or alter prescribed medication without
                speaking with your physician or prescribing healthcare
                professional. Homeopathic consultations do not replace
                necessary licensed medical care.
              </p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details>
            <summary>
              <span>Do you work with children and families?</span>
              <span class="faq-symbol" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
            </summary>

            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>
                Yes. Children and adults can receive individualized homeopathic
                consultations. A parent or legal guardian participates in a
                child&rsquo;s case and provides relevant health history and
                observations.
              </p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details>
            <summary>
              <span>What happens during follow-up appointments?</span>
              <span class="faq-symbol" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
            </summary>

            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>
                Follow-up appointments focus on what has changed since the
                remedy was taken. Improvements, new symptoms, returning
                symptoms, energy, sleep, emotional well-being, and overall
                resilience may all help guide the next decision.
              </p>
            </div>
          </details>

        </div>

        <div class="faq-link">
          <Button href="/faq" variant="gold">
            Explore All Frequently Asked Questions
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Final call to action -->
    <section class="consultation-cta">
      <div class="cta-inner">
        <p class="eyebrow">Take the Next Step</p>

        <h2>Ready to begin your healing journey?</h2>

        <SectionDivider />

        <p>
          Whether you are simply exploring homeopathy or feel ready to begin
          care, Mindy would be honored to listen to your story and help you
          understand the next step.
        </p>

        <div class="cta-actions">
          <Button
            href={scheduleUrl}
            target="_blank"
            variant="primary"
          >
            Schedule Through Homeopathy Help Network
          </Button>

          <Button href={contactEmail} variant="gold">
            Contact Mindy
          </Button>
        </div>

        <p class="supervision-note">
          Consultations are provided as part of Mindy&rsquo;s supervised
          clinical internship through Homeopathy Help Network.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
<style>
  main {
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /*
   * Shared typography
   */

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 17px;

    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1,
  h2,
  h3 {
    color: var(--navy);
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0;

    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 6.3vw, 5.8rem);
    line-height: 0.98;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0;

    font-size: clamp(2.7rem, 4.7vw, 4.05rem);
    line-height: 1.06;
  }

  h3 {
    margin: 0;

    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.65rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .divider-wrap,
  .divider-left {
    width: max-content;
  }

  .divider-wrap {
    margin: 28px auto;
  }

  .divider-left {
    margin-top: 28px;
  }

  /*
   * Hero
   */

  .consultation-hero {
    padding: 90px 40px 105px;

    background:
      radial-gradient(
        circle at top,
        #fffdf8 0%,
        #f7efe3 58%,
        #ecddc8 100%
      );

    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero-copy {
    max-width: 790px;
    margin: 0 auto;

    color: #40516a;
    font-size: 1.27rem;
    line-height: 1.88;
  }

  .hero-actions,
  .cta-actions {
    margin-top: 40px;

    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /*
   * Hahnemann quote
   */

  .quote-section {
    padding: 72px 40px;

    background: #fffdf9;
  }

  .quote-inner {
    position: relative;

    max-width: 1040px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px 110px 18px;

    text-align: center;
  }

  .quote-inner blockquote {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .quote-inner blockquote p {
    margin: 0;

    color: var(--navy);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.65rem);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .quote-inner cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 22px;

    color: #756b5c;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    font-style: normal;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .quote-mark {
    position: absolute;

    color: rgba(184, 154, 94, 0.22);
    font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
    font-size: 9rem;
    line-height: 1;

    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .quote-mark-open {
    left: 90;
    top: -20px;
  }

  .quote-mark-close-inline {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-left: 0.08em;

  color: rgba(184, 154, 94, 0.22);
  font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
  font-size: 2.15em;
  font-style: normal;
  line-height: 0;

  vertical-align: -0.3em;

  pointer-events: none;
  user-select: none;
}

  /*
   * Difference
   */

  .difference-section {
    padding: 112px 40px;

    background:
      radial-gradient(
        circle at top left,
        #fcf8f0 0%,
        #f2e7d7 100%
      );
  }

  .difference-inner {
    max-width: 1160px;
    margin: 0 auto;

    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
    gap: 86px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .difference-copy {
    color: #3f5068;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.92;
  }

  .difference-copy p {
    margin: 0 0 27px;
  }

  .difference-copy p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .difference-copy .emphasis {
    padding: 24px 28px;

    background: rgba(255, 253, 249, 0.58);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: 0 18px 18px 0;

    color: var(--navy);
    font-size: 1.22rem;
    font-style: italic;

    box-shadow:
      0 14px 34px rgba(16, 35, 63, 0.05);
  }

  /*
   * Process introduction
   */

  .process-intro {
    padding: 108px 40px 74px;

    background: #fffdf9;

    text-align: center;
  }

  .process-intro-inner {
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .process-intro-inner h2 {
    margin-bottom: 27px;
  }

  .process-intro-inner > p:last-child {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 31px auto 0;

    color: #40516a;
    font-size: 1.18rem;
    line-height: 1.88;
  }

  /*
   * Timeline
   */

  .timeline-section {
    padding: 30px 40px 122px;

    background: #fffdf9;
  }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;

    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: "";

    position: absolute;
    top: 42px;
    bottom: 42px;
    left: 50%;

    width: 2px;

    background:
      linear-gradient(
        180deg,
        rgba(184, 154, 94, 0.04),
        rgba(184, 154, 94, 0.74) 12%,
        rgba(184, 154, 94, 0.74) 88%,
        rgba(184, 154, 94, 0.04)
      );

    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }

  .timeline-step {
    position: relative;

    width: 50%;
    margin-bottom: 86px;
  }

  .timeline-step:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .step-left {
    padding-right: 68px;
  }

  .step-right {
    margin-left: 50%;
    padding-left: 68px;
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 2;
    top: 31px;

    width: 58px;
    height: 58px;

    display: grid;
    place-items: center;

    background:
      linear-gradient(
        145deg,
        #fffdf8,
        #f4e8d5
      );

    border: 1px solid rgba(184, 154, 94, 0.84);
    border-radius: 50%;

    box-shadow:
      0 10px 28px rgba(16, 35, 63, 0.09);
  }

  .step-left .timeline-marker {
    right: -29px;
  }

  .step-right .timeline-marker {
    left: -29px;
  }

  .timeline-marker span {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
    font-size: 1.18rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .step-card {
    padding: 39px 39px 37px;

    background:
      linear-gradient(
        145deg,
        #fffaf2,
        #f7eddf
      );

    border: 1px solid #e4d6bf;
    border-radius: 25px;

    box-shadow:
      0 18px 45px rgba(16, 35, 63, 0.07);

    transition:
      transform 0.28s ease,
      box-shadow 0.28s ease,
      border-color 0.28s ease;
  }

  .step-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);

    border-color: rgba(184, 154, 94, 0.48);

    box-shadow:
      0 26px 60px rgba(16, 35, 63, 0.115);
  }

  .step-heading {
    margin-bottom: 17px;

    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .step-label,
  .step-duration {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .step-label {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .step-duration {
    color: #756b5c;
    font-size: 0.83rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .step-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 21px;
  }

  .step-card > p {
    margin: 0 0 20px;

    color: #46566d;
    font-size: 1.04rem;
    line-height: 1.78;
  }

  .step-card ul {
    margin: 5px 0 23px;
    padding-left: 22px;

    color: #46566d;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.72;
  }

  .step-card li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    padding-left: 4px;
  }

  .step-card li::marker {
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .two-column-list {
    columns: 2;
    column-gap: 28px;
  }

  .step-card .step-note {
    margin: 23px 0 0;
    padding: 17px 20px;

    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.42);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: 0 13px 13px 0;

    color: #32445f;
    font-size: 0.94rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .principles {
    margin: 25px 0;

    display: flex;
    gap: 9px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .principles span {
    padding: 8px 13px;

    color: #7b5f1b;
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;

    background: rgba(184, 154, 94, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(184, 154, 94, 0.28);
    border-radius: 999px;
  }

  /*
   * Is classical homeopathy right for me?
   */

  .right-for-me {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;

    padding: 116px 40px;

    background:
